{"word":"Day","slug":"day","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Day</b> A creative period<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=5'>Gen 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=8'>Gen 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=13'>Gen 1:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=19'>Gen 1:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=23'>Gen 1:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=31'>Gen 1:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=2'>Gen 2:2</a><br/> Divided into twelve hours<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=9'>Joh 11:9</a><br/> Prophetic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=3&verse=8'>2Pe 3:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=8&verse=14'>Dan 8:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=9&verse=27'>Dan 9:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=12&verse=12'>Dan 12:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=11&verse=3'>Rev 11:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=9&verse=15'>Rev 9:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=12&verse=6'>Rev 12:6</a><br/> Six working days ordained<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=20&verse=9'>Exo 20:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=46&verse=1'>Eze 46:1</a><br/> Sixth day of the week called preparation day<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=42'>Mar 15:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=14'>Joh 19:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=31'>Joh 19:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=42'>Joh 19:42</a><br/> First day of the week called the Lord's day<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=1&verse=10'>Rev 1:10</a><br/> Day's journey, eighteen or twenty miles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=18'>Exo 3:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=4'>1Ki 19:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=3&verse=4'>Jon 3:4</a><br/> Sabbath day's journey, about two thousand paces<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=12'>Act 1:12</a><br/><a href='S:Sabbath'>Sabbath</a><br/> Times of adversity called &#187;Day of the Lord&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=2&verse=12'>Isa 2:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=13&verse=6'>Isa 13:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=13&verse=9'>Isa 13:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=34&verse=8'>Isa 34:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=46&verse=10'>Jer 46:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=2&verse=22'>Lam 2:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=30&verse=3'>Eze 30:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=5&verse=18'>Amo 5:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=2&verse=1'>Joe 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&verse=15'>Oba 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=1&verse=8'>Zep 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=1&verse=18'>Zep 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=2&verse=3'>Zep 2:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=14&verse=1'>Zec 14:1</a><br/> Judgment<br/> - Called Day of the Lord<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=4&verse=5'>Mal 4:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=5&verse=5'>1Co 5:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=1&verse=14'>2Co 1:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=5&verse=2'>1Th 5:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=3&verse=10'>2Pe 3:10</a><br/><a href='S:Judgment'>Judgment</a> <br/> A figure of spiritual illumination<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=4&verse=18'>Pro 4:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=5&verse=8'>1Th 5:8</a>"}]}